07:39.259 --> 07:41.061 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
But today is a new day.

07:41.094 --> 07:45.332 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: In the end,
three Democrats,
Joe Manchin, Heidi Heitkamp, and
Joe Donnelly,

07:45.365 --> 07:47.834 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
joined Republicans in supporting
Gorsuch.

07:47.867 --> 07:51.338 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
