Durbin, lamented
how it came to be.

07:51.371 --> 07:53.206 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

07:53.239 --> 07:55.875 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
RICHARD DURBIN (D-IL), Minority
Whip: When
the rule was changed, some
senators were engaged

07:55.909 --> 07:59.446 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
