the Senate and
the House.

08:49.896 --> 08:52.599 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: On that at
least, Schumer
and McConnell agreed.

08:52.632 --> 08:54.434 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

08:54.467 --> 08:57.003 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MITCH MCCONNELL: This notion
that this somehow
bleeds over into the legislative
filibuster

08:57.036 --> 08:58.004 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
is untrue.

08:58.037 --> 08:59.773 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
I'm opposed to it.

08:59.806 --> 09:03.276 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: As for Judge
Gorsuch, his
swearing-in as the 101st
associate justice

09:03.309 --> 09:06.746 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
of the U.S. Supreme Court is set
for Monday.

