More than 50,000 people marched
in cities
across South Africa today to
protest government

09:57.697 --> 09:59.566 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
corruption.

09:59.599 --> 10:04.404 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
They carried signs and shouted
slogans demanding
the removal of President Jacob
Zuma, after

10:04.437 --> 10:08.241 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
