anti-corruption finance
minister.

10:08.274 --> 10:15.014 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WOMAN: I am marching because I
have a 4-year-old
daughter, and I feel if I don't
do something

10:15.048 --> 10:17.717 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
