33:39.351 --> 33:40.485 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: David?

33:40.518 --> 33:42.487 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DAVID BROOKS: Well, it's not my
preferred
strategy.

33:42.520 --> 33:44.422 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
